# Root Cause Summary View

The dashboard should highlight the highest confidence RCA.

Example:

```
--------------------------------------

Primary Root Cause

ETHERNET_FAILURE


Confidence:

92%


Reason:

Interface failure occurred before
dependent network failures.


--------------------------------------
```

---

# Evidence Explorer

Engineers should be able to drill down.

Example:

```
Root Cause:

ETHERNET_FAILURE


Evidence:


File:

kernel.log


Line:

245


Message:

NETDEV WATCHDOG timeout
```

