# AI Assisted RCA

Future integration:

```
              report.json

                   |

                   v

             AI Reasoning Layer

                   |

                   v

       Human-readable RCA Explanation
```

Example:

Input:

```
Ethernet link failures detected
before DHCP failures.
```

AI output:

```
The most probable root cause is an Ethernet
interface failure. DHCP failures appear to be
secondary symptoms caused by loss of connectivity.
```

